5. **Governance & Service Delivery** (13): Aao Khud Ko Parkhein, Alert, Dastavez, Shreshth, Project SARAL, Project Handy, Jandarshan, Call Centre, BPO, Project Susashan Rath, Project sugaam, Team Prahari, Sampoorna
